---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import GetQuoete from "../../../components/buttons/GetQuote.astro";
import Testimonials from "../../../components/Testimonials";
import { FaStar } from "react-icons/fa";
import ButtonScrollTop from "../../../components/buttons/ButtonScrollTop";
---

<style>
  .custom-background {
    background:
      linear-gradient(hsla(250, 75%, 5%, 0.5), rgba(6, 3, 21, 0.5)),
      url("/img/reseller.webp") center center no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
  }

  .footer--img {
    background-image: url("/public/img/footer.webp");
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
  }
</style>

<Layout title="Auto Transport For Car Reseller | Cayad Auto Transport">
  <div
    class="container-fluid flex flex-col items-center justify-center custom-background h-[60vh]"
  >
    <div class="w-[80%]">
      <h1
        class="text-white text-[4rem] xs:text-[1.8rem] sm:text-[1.8rem] font-bold"
      >
        Auto transport tips for car resellers
      </h1>
      <p class="text-white text-lg font-semibold">
        Cayad Auto Transport delivers resold cars to new owners
      </p>
      <button
        class="flex mt-4 min-w-[250px] max-w-[270px] items-center justify-center border mb-2 border-transparent bg-btn-blue px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white hover:bg-btn-hover transition-colors duration-500 ease-in-out focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
      >
        <a href="/quote/">Get a Quote</a>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 flex justify-center mb-8">
    <Testimonials title="Our Customers Say" client:load />
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col xs:flex-col sm:flex-col items-center h-max w-full">
    <div class="w-[80%] xs:w-[100%] sm:w-[100%] px-4">
      <div
        class="grid mt-8 grid-cols-2 xs:grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-1 w-full gap-6"
      >
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0 hover:shadow-xl duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.3s"
        >
          <h5 class="mb-2 py-4 text-xl text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold">
            Save time
          </h5>
          <p class="py-4" style="text-align: justify;">
            When you are selling a car, speed and convenience are crucial for
            your business. Cayad Auto Transport is proven for saving time for
            both car resellers and buyers by scheduling convenient pick-ups and
            deliveries.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 hover:shadow-xl duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.5s"
        >
          <div class="team-item p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0">
            <h5 class="mb-2 py-4 text-xl text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold">
              Secure delivery
            </h5>
            <p class="py-4" style="text-align: justify;">
              Rest assured that any vehicles sold are traveling safely to their
              new homes. Cayad Auto Transport can deliver your vehicle
              nationwide with secure Door to door open or enclosed transport.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 hover:shadow-xl duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.7s"
        >
          <div class="team-item p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0">
            <h5 class="mb-2 py-4 text-xl text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold">
              Best Prices
            </h5>
            <p class="py-4" style="text-align: justify;">
              we offer competitive prices for a high quality service. Our team
              will give you a comprehensive quote online with no hidden fees or
              extra taxes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 hover:shadow-xl duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.9s"
        >
          <div class="team-item p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0">
            <h5 class="mb-2 text-xl py-4 text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold">
              Insurance provided
            </h5>
            <p class="py-4" style="text-align: justify;">
              Ship with us worry-free knowing that your vehicle will be insured
              from the time it’s picked up to the time it’s delivered.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <h1 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold text-[2.5rem]">
      Why should you choose Cayad Auto Transport for your car shipment?
    </h1>
    <div
      class="w-[80%] mt-8 xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex justify-between"
    >
      <div class="w-[50%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:mb-8 sm:mb-8">
        <div class="mt-8">
          <h3 class="text-[1.5rem] font-bold">Top rated company</h3>
          <p class="text-base mt-8">
            We have earned our place on the Inc. 500 list as one of the top 500
            fastest growing companies in America. We are also proud of our A+
            rating with the BBB for good business practices. We’ve also received
            many 5-star ratings on Transport Reviews and My Moving Reviews for
            customer service and satisfaction.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <h3 class="text-[1.5rem] font-bold">‌Easy shipping process ​</h3>
          <p class="text-base mt-4">
            Shipping cars is all we do. We have a simple four-step process that
            works for any possible car shipment situation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-[40%] xs:w-[100%] sm:w-[100%]">
        <img src="/img/car-man.webp" class="rounded-xl" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex justify-between"
    >
      <div class="w-[40%] xs:w-[100%] sm:w-[100%]">
        <img src="/img/car-man1.webp" class="rounded-xl" />
      </div>
      <div class="w-[50%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:mb-8 sm:mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-bold text-base">
          Returning customer discount
        </h1>
        <p class="text-base mt-4">
          Cayad Auto Transport has special discounts for repeat customers, so
          don’t hesitate to schedule your car shipment with us repeatedly.
        </p>

        <h1 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-bold mt-8 text-base">
          Excellent communication
        </h1>
        <p class="text-base mt-4">
          We are here 7 days a week for extended hours to keep you up to date
          with the status of your order and the location of your vehicle.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="w-full flex mb-8 flex-col items-center xs:min-w-[100%] xs:px-0 sm:min-w-[100%] sm:px-0 mx-auto overflow-hidden px-0"
  >
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:min-w-[100%] xs:px-4 sm:min-w-[100%] sm:px-4 py-10 px-0"
    >
      <h1 class="text-4xl text-[#19171fd2] font-medium mb-10">
        Why should you choose Cayad Auto Transport for car resellers?
      </h1>
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-1 xs:grid-cols-1 gap-10"
      >
        <div class="wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <img src="/img/dollar.webp" class="w-24 h-20 mb-2" />
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold">Competitive Prices</h5>
              <p class="text-justify xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0">
                Cayad Auto Transport understands the importance of providing
                competitive prices for car resellers. We offer affordable and
                transparent pricing options that are tailored to meet the unique
                needs of car resellers. Our pricing structure ensures that you
                receive a fair and cost-effective solution for shipping multiple
                vehicles. By choosing us, you can trust that you are getting the
                best value for your money.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <img src="/img/easy.webp" class="w-24 h-20 mb-2" />
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold">Ease of Use</h5>
              <p class="text-justify xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0">
                We prioritize ease of use for our car reseller customers. Our
                user-friendly online platform allows you to easily request a
                quote, schedule pickups, and track the progress of your
                shipments. We streamline the entire process to save you time and
                effort, ensuring a smooth and efficient shipping experience. Our
                goal is to make it as convenient as possible for you to
                transport your vehicles to your customers.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
            <img src="/img/call.webp" class="w-24 h-24 mb-2" />
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold">Exceptional Staff Assistance</h5>
              <p class="text-justify xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0">
                Our dedicated team is committed to providing exceptional
                assistance to car resellers. We understand the unique
                requirements and time-sensitive nature of your business. Our
                knowledgeable staff is available to guide you through the entire
                shipping process, from helping you choose the right shipping
                options to providing updates on the status of your shipments. We
                are here to support you and ensure a seamless and hassle-free
                experience.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-[95%] wow"
          data-aos="fade-right"
          data-aos-delay="100"
          style="min-height: 400px;"
        >
          <div class="h-full">
            <img
              src="/img/reseller.webp"
              class="object-cover rounded w-full h-full"
              alt=""
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="fixed bottom-4 right-20 flex flex-col items-end">
    <ButtonScrollTop client:load />
  </div>
</Layout>
